-- AbitibiBowater Inc. Signs Agreement on Pensions With Ontario Government
-- B y   S t e v e n   F r o m m
-- 2010-11-19T15:03:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-19/abitibibowater-inc-signs-agreement-on-pensions-with-ontario-government.html
AbitibiBowater Inc. said it had
entered into agreements with the government of Ontario related
to funding relief in respect of the material aggregate solvency
deficits in the registered pension plans the company sponsors in
Ontario and Quebec.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Fromm at 
 sfromm@bloomberg.net  